{"tid":489673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女大學生報警指控迷姦, 最後反被控偷竊","createTime":"2017-12-05T02:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T06:32:58.000Z","uid":134071,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"46bdb3ba17a6afc418249b263bee9dbffc03b077","tid":489673,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20170704/56911080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170704%2F56911080&d=9XfMOBse%2BFxN9d%2B%2Faax2U7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=50e2c3d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170704%2F56911080&h=3d5422ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20170704/56911080</a><br />\n<br />\n家長怒告警察同大學<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0704 19:31<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國阿拉巴馬大學（University of Alabama）一名女生疑被迷姦後報警，警方經調查後不但沒有起訴涉案男子，還反指女生從對方家中取走了一支槍。女生其後精神狀態轉差退學，去年自殺身亡。</strong>女生的父母近日入稟法院，指警員和校方職員等人處理事件不當，導致女兒抑鬱自殺，亦控告涉案男子。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，當年20歲的朗登尼（Megan Rondini）原本計劃讀醫科，她2015年7月在酒吧認識了一名男子，然後在對方住所疑被落藥，之後被人強姦。<br />\n<br />\n警察調查案件時集中調查朗登尼，指她從男子的住所取走一支手槍和3美元（23.4港元）的車資，「朗登尼最後被視為犯人，她在性罪行案件中的受害人身份完全被忽略」。入稟狀亦指控校方沒有向朗登尼提供心理輔導。<br />\n<br />\n涉案男子最後沒有被檢控，朗登尼的父母指調查人員和大學方面處理不當，導致她患上抑鬱、焦慮和創傷後遺症，最後她踏上自殺的不歸路。校方拒絕回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社／美國《紐約每日新聞》"},{"pid":"63d21a1a6f605ccd22b8dd0e64926541cf530c16","tid":489673,"uid":134474,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔:今次有報警都係臭雞一名/勞資"},{"pid":"b24646abd3251ca89e0dead9dd8d065d8066ee75","tid":489673,"uid":127123,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:09:18.000Z","msg":"係酒吧識人仲要單獨上人屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280fc92141602a80a51e7a673e7027accfcb7c61","tid":489673,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔:今次有報警都係臭雞一名/勞資</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「最後抑鬱自殺而死, 都係雞」"},{"pid":"eb1ca90252578bc0af1c1becb1ea506bd93f99ae","tid":489673,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e643a64d0e4c0bc60e86e147bec721bd2811b829","tid":489673,"uid":132981,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"在酒吧認識了一名男子..... <br />\n<br />\n.....臭雞 !"},{"pid":"cd51a283e6a5b35e3a492295eb04a568fd702c5f","tid":489673,"uid":94388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:30:24.000Z","msg":"咁搞法遲早有真強姦案果陣個個都wfc"},{"pid":"34d13c06e5f3e1ba86f79e05355140d1cdfd0015","tid":489673,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁搞法遲早有真強姦案果陣個個都wfc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家警方咪wfc, 女生最後抑鬱自殺"},{"pid":"f73ba6dac9d27ccef09d649664c173c3487594cd","tid":489673,"uid":40932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁搞法遲早有真強姦案果陣個個都wfc</blockquote><br />\n個個都利用自己有西，抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54af3f19d5ea5fbf9ac036c110e7605c29d0dbf","tid":489673,"uid":40932,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁搞法遲早有真強姦案果陣個個都wfc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家警方咪wfc, 女生最後抑鬱自殺</blockquote><br />\n邊到指出警方wfc<br />\n判得唔乎合女方就wfc<br />\n自殺仲係要隔左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同本身件事有無直接關係都唔知"},{"pid":"77504944c9494429143e42d926255a8deba3006e","tid":489673,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁搞法遲早有真強姦案果陣個個都wfc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家警方咪wfc, 女生最後抑鬱自殺</